<div class="features detailed-features">
  <div class="feats">
    <div class="feat">
      <i class="icon fa fa-code-fork"></i>
      <h2>All Platforms in One Go</h2>
      <p>
        One source code for all platforms simultaneously: desktop/mobile website, native mobile apps.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <i class="icon fa fa-gamepad"></i>
      <h2>Quasar Play App</h2>
      <p>
        Develop Apps with Hot Reload directly on your phone.
        <a class="playstore" style="margin-left: -11px;" href='https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.quasarframework.quasarplay&utm_source=global_co&utm_medium=prtnr&utm_content=Mar2515&utm_campaign=PartBadge&pcampaignid=MKT-Other-global-all-co-prtnr-py-PartBadge-Mar2515-1'><img alt='Get it on Google Play' src='https://play.google.com/intl/en_us/badges/images/generic/en_badge_web_generic.png'/></a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <i class="icon fa fa-thumbs-o-up"></i>
      <h2>VueJs & ES6</h2>
      <p>
        ES6 Javascript. Leverage VueJs & NPM ecosystem easily. Support for *.vue single file components.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="feat">
      <i class="icon fa fa-hourglass-half"></i>
      <h2>Boilerplate</h2>
      <p>
        Out of the box App code boilerplate, build system, hot reload, linter, test setup, auto minification and more.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <i class="icon fa fa-bolt"></i>
      <h2>Speed & Efficiency</h2>
      <p>
        Quasar focuses on low memory footprint, efficiency and making Apps run really fast.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <i class="icon fa fa-arrows-alt"></i>
      <h2>Wide Support</h2>
      <p>iOS, Android, Windows Phone, Blackberry, Google Chrome, Firefox, IE/Edge.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <i class="icon fa fa-magic"></i>
      <h2>Themes</h2>
      <p>
        Full-featured Quasar CSS Framework. <strong>Material Design</strong> and <strong>iOS</strong> themes included.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <i class="icon fa fa-refresh"></i>
      <h2>Dev Hot Reload</h2>
      <p>
        More than just Live Reload. Preserve App state while updating in the browser.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <i class="icon fa fa-gears"></i>
      <h2>Built-in Components</h2>
      <p>
        Leverage large variety of built-in VueJs Quasar components which do most of the heavy-lifting of your App.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <i class="icon fa fa-book"></i>
      <h2>Great Documentation</h2>
      <p>
        Crystal clear documentation with examples, guides, tips and demos with source code available.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <i class="icon fa fa-github"></i>
      <h2>Open Source</h2>
      <p>
        Visit <strong><a href="<%- config.github %>" target="_blank">Github <i class="fa fa-github"></i></a></strong> page.
        Contributions under any form are welcomed.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

